                            <div id="helpinfo">
                                This option is about how to define associated data records.
                                <br>
                                '<b>Any overlap</b>': when an input region shares at least 1bp with either interactors
                                of a record.
                                <br>
                                '<b>Center overlap</b>': when center of an input region falls into either interactor of
                                a record, or vice versa.
